[
    {
        "text": "The martini!",
        "startTime": 2001,
        "endTime": 2777,
        "slowStartTime": 3152,
        "slowEndTime": 4391
    },
    {
        "text": "The martini is the ultimate cool and sophisticated drink.",
        "startTime": 3384,
        "endTime": 6396,
        "slowStartTime": 5226,
        "slowEndTime": 9819
    },
    {
        "text": "Sipping a martini from a stemmed, cocktail glass makes everyone feel a bit James Bondish...",
        "startTime": 7041,
        "endTime": 11961,
        "slowStartTime": 10712,
        "slowEndTime": 18166
    },
    {
        "text": "...who, by the way, likes his martini shaken, not stirred.",
        "startTime": 12516,
        "endTime": 15486,
        "slowStartTime": 18924,
        "slowEndTime": 23454
    },
    {
        "text": "Where and how the first martini came to be is pure libation lore.",
        "startTime": 17503,
        "endTime": 21653,
        "slowStartTime": 26404,
        "slowEndTime": 32705
    },
    {
        "text": "One story, in 1849, has a successful prospect walking into a bar and ordering a drink.",
        "startTime": 21983,
        "endTime": 27981,
        "slowStartTime": 33125,
        "slowEndTime": 42196
    },
    {
        "text": "The bartender fixes him a Martinez special which later became the martini.",
        "startTime": 28611,
        "endTime": 32795,
        "slowStartTime": 43066,
        "slowEndTime": 49417
    },
    {
        "text": "Another story in the 1860s, a cocktail called the Martinez...",
        "startTime": 33299,
        "endTime": 37215,
        "slowStartTime": 50098,
        "slowEndTime": 56048
    },
    {
        "text": "...was created in the Occidental Hotel in San Francisco.",
        "startTime": 37292,
        "endTime": 39922,
        "slowStartTime": 56088,
        "slowEndTime": 60108
    },
    {
        "text": "The hotel was near the porch to the town of Martinez.",
        "startTime": 40125,
        "endTime": 42663,
        "slowStartTime": 60338,
        "slowEndTime": 64220
    },
    {
        "text": "We do know that in the late 19th century,...",
        "startTime": 43071,
        "endTime": 45113,
        "slowStartTime": 64757,
        "slowEndTime": 67894
    },
    {
        "text": "...bartending guides featured drinks with similar names and ingredients.",
        "startTime": 45281,
        "endTime": 48621,
        "slowStartTime": 68072,
        "slowEndTime": 73157
    },
    {
        "text": "Martinis have always had an edgy air about them,...",
        "startTime": 48877,
        "endTime": 51129,
        "slowStartTime": 73466,
        "slowEndTime": 76918
    },
    {
        "text": "...which maybe why James Bond found them so appealing.",
        "startTime": 51248,
        "endTime": 53701,
        "slowStartTime": 77022,
        "slowEndTime": 80777
    },
    {
        "text": "This maybe due to the fact that illegal and easy gin manufacturing during Prohibition,...",
        "startTime": 54107,
        "endTime": 58377,
        "slowStartTime": 81311,
        "slowEndTime": 87790
    },
    {
        "text": "...made the martini one of the predominant cocktails.",
        "startTime": 58747,
        "endTime": 60778,
        "slowStartTime": 88270,
        "slowEndTime": 91392
    },
    {
        "text": "Classic martinis are made with just three ingredients:...",
        "startTime": 61130,
        "endTime": 63380,
        "slowStartTime": 91845,
        "slowEndTime": 95295
    },
    {
        "text": "...gin, vermouth, which can be either dry or sweet,...",
        "startTime": 63563,
        "endTime": 66379,
        "slowStartTime": 95494,
        "slowEndTime": 99793
    },
    {
        "text": "...and a garnish, typically a green olive or a twist of lemon peel.",
        "startTime": 66896,
        "endTime": 70207,
        "slowStartTime": 100494,
        "slowEndTime": 105536
    },
    {
        "text": "The measurement of these ingredients is up for grabs.",
        "startTime": 71009,
        "endTime": 73345,
        "slowStartTime": 106663,
        "slowEndTime": 110242
    },
    {
        "text": "Martini aficionados are positively finicky about how their martinis were made.",
        "startTime": 74169,
        "endTime": 78177,
        "slowStartTime": 111404,
        "slowEndTime": 117490
    },
    {
        "text": "The biggest area of contention is around how dry or how wet your martini is.",
        "startTime": 79250,
        "endTime": 83463,
        "slowStartTime": 119025,
        "slowEndTime": 125419
    },
    {
        "text": "The less vermouth, the drier.",
        "startTime": 84286,
        "endTime": 85681,
        "slowStartTime": 126579,
        "slowEndTime": 128747
    },
    {
        "text": "The more vermouth you have, the wetter the martini.",
        "startTime": 86757,
        "endTime": 89041,
        "slowStartTime": 130285,
        "slowEndTime": 133786
    },
    {
        "text": "Here's how you make the martini:...",
        "startTime": 90350,
        "endTime": 91528,
        "slowStartTime": 135675,
        "slowEndTime": 137517
    },
    {
        "text": "...fill a cocktail shaker with ice cubes, add gin, add vermouth,...",
        "startTime": 92067,
        "endTime": 96119,
        "slowStartTime": 138251,
        "slowEndTime": 144403
    },
    {
        "text": "...shake or stir,...",
        "startTime": 96777,
        "endTime": 97636,
        "slowStartTime": 145315,
        "slowEndTime": 146679
    },
    {
        "text": "...pour the martini in the chilled cocktail glasses, add garnish, and serve.",
        "startTime": 98527,
        "endTime": 102118,
        "slowStartTime": 147940,
        "slowEndTime": 153402
    },
    {
        "text": "Drink martini straight up, which means without ice.",
        "startTime": 103206,
        "endTime": 106016,
        "slowStartTime": 154959,
        "slowEndTime": 159249
    },
    {
        "text": "Dry or wet, shaken or stirred, go classic tonight with the martini.",
        "startTime": 106434,
        "endTime": 110110,
        "slowStartTime": 159801,
        "slowEndTime": 165390
    },
    {
        "text": "Evening wear is optional.",
        "startTime": 110365,
        "endTime": 111430,
        "slowStartTime": 165697,
        "slowEndTime": 167370
    }
]